This repository contains a Java project demonstrating the use of JDBC PreparedStatement for performing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on a MySQL database. The LearnJdbcPs class includes methods to:

Insert a product record into the Products table using PreparedStatement.
Retrieve product details based on product_id.
Update the price and quantity of an existing product.
Delete a product using its product_id.
Database Connection Details:

Database Name: learnjdbc
MySQL Credentials: Username: root, Password: yash
The project assumes that the MySQL server is running locally at port 3306.
Technologies Used:

Java (JDBC API)
MySQL Database
This project aims to illustrate safe and efficient database operations using PreparedStatement, which helps in preventing SQL injection and ensures proper handling of SQL queries.
